Pablo y Violeta get into the car
Pablo and Violeta together make about $40,000 a year
canning, but this is not the most interesting thing about
them. Their love story could be a romantic novel. A few
spoilers: teenage love in rural Mexico, separation from
a child, two difficult marriages, and an effervescent love
revamped while collecting empty soda containers. Their
honeymoon will be their retirement, in the house they
bought in Mexico, to the tune of five cents at a time.
